This paper deals with privacy issues in search logs, which involves topics related to security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and cryptography (cs.CY). The paper discusses algorithms for publishing search logs while preserving privacy, which is a common concern in these sub-fields. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
